# Spec-Driven Development

This project uses **Spec-Driven Development** for non-trivial features.

## When to Use This Skill

- Planning a new feature
- Implementing from a specification
- Reviewing implementation

## Workflow

1. Create spec in `specs/XXX-feature-name/` (spec.md, plan.md, tasks.md)
2. Review and refine the spec
3. Implement following TDD
4. Code review
5. Track progress in `tasks.md` and `_todo.md`
